Title: Unknown capability to add: "CAP_CAP_SYS_PTRACE"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: helm
Date: 1659105397
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 1.1.0

When deploying the helm chart on Kubernetes clusters which run with docker
version <= 19.02 or containerd version <= 1.4.4, the deployment would fail with
an error message reading '[...] Unknown capability to add:
"CAP_CAP_SYS_PTRACE"'. This has been fixed.
